Basic architecture
  C++ main process
  OpenGL rendering + SDL event loop
   Game state is updated inside of python
   Renderer is implemented in C++ for speed

main loop:
  get user input + handle relevant callbacks
  get packets from network + handle callbacks
  check for time since last tick/update and send if required

chunk cache:
  in-memory cache of chunks
  only chunks within configured draw distance shown

app state and sub state:
  overall state: menu/ingame/whatever
  paused boolean
  ingame:
    flying/walking/running
    
